Interface CoreFoundation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.Library

    public interface CoreFoundation
extends com.sun.jna.Library
    CoreFoundation framework for power supply stats. This class should be considered non-API as it may be removed if/when its code is incorporated into the JNA project.
    Author:
